    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Paper"><a href="#Paper" class="headerlink" title="Paper:"></a>Paper:</h3><h3 id="A-Novel-Distance-Measure-for-Comparing-Long-Time-Series"><a href="#A-Novel-Distance-Measure-for-Comparing-Long-Time-Series" class="headerlink" title="A Novel Distance Measure for Comparing Long Time Series"></a>A Novel Distance Measure for Comparing Long Time Series</h3><h4 id="Author"><a href="#Author" class="headerlink" title="Author:"></a>Author:</h4><h4 id="Audrey-Der-Chin-Chia-Michael-Yeh-Renjie-Wu-Junpeng-Wang-Yan-Zheng-Zhongfang-Zhuang-Liang-Wang-Wei-Zhang-Eamonn-Keogh"><a href="#Audrey-Der-Chin-Chia-Michael-Yeh-Renjie-Wu-Junpeng-Wang-Yan-Zheng-Zhongfang-Zhuang-Liang-Wang-Wei-Zhang-Eamonn-Keogh" class="headerlink" title="Audrey Der, Chin-Chia Michael Yeh, Renjie Wu, Junpeng Wang, Yan Zheng, Zhongfang Zhuang, Liang Wang, Wei Zhang, Eamonn Keogh"></a>Audrey Der, Chin-Chia Michael Yeh, Renjie Wu, Junpeng Wang, Yan Zheng, Zhongfang Zhuang, Liang Wang, Wei Zhang, Eamonn Keogh</h4><hr><hr><h4 id="Definition"><a href="#Definition" class="headerlink" title="Definition"></a>Definition</h4><ul><li>TIME SERIES &amp; SUBSEQUENCE</li></ul><p><a href="https://postimg.cc/2Lb4gnD6"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/7hXmGNtg/1.png" alt="1.png"></a></p><p><a href="https://postimg.cc/ThV2Jpmq"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/gc5wdh25/Screenshot-2023-07-22-at-17-33-32.png" alt="Screenshot-2023-07-22-at-17-33-32.png"></a></p><p>There is an another definition</p><p><a href="https://postimg.cc/LqZKFGhR"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/N0dgmccy/Screenshot-2023-07-23-at-13-38-17.png" alt="Screenshot-2023-07-23-at-13-38-17.png"></a></p><ul><li>DICTIONARYS</li></ul><p><a href="https://postimg.cc/MMsC9J6w"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/d3vJtJgh/Screenshot-2023-07-22-at-17-37-42.png" alt="Screenshot-2023-07-22-at-17-37-42.png"></a></p><ul><li></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    
